/home/python/pyenv/versions/scrapy-python/bin/pip
/home/python/pyenv/versions/scrapy-python/bin/python

## 切换到虚拟环境
pyenv activate scrapy-python

## 创建项目：
在scrapy-spider目录下创建tutorial项目
scrapy startproject tutorial scrapy-spider

or

/home/python/pyenv/versions/2.7.12/envs/scrapy-python/bin/scrapy startproject tutorial scrapy-spider


## 启动爬虫
scrapy crawl huxiu
or
/home/python/pyenv/versions/2.7.12/envs/scrapy-python/bin/scrapy crawl huxiu
